hit my personal rock bottom.

00:05:17.130 --> 00:05:24.730 align:middle line:84%
But it was really just
swallowing all my pride.

00:05:24.730 --> 00:05:27.550 align:middle line:90%


00:05:27.550 --> 00:05:31.390 align:middle line:84%
