00:05:44.910 --> 00:05:49.310 align:middle line:84%
I started taking the steps
required in order to live

00:05:49.310 --> 00:05:53.670 align:middle line:90%
a successful, effective life.

00:05:53.670 --> 00:05:58.230 align:middle line:84%
After just a little
bit of sobriety,

00:05:58.230 --> 00:06:01.470 align:middle line:90%
I gained back a lot of strength.

00:06:01.470 --> 00:06:03.444 align:middle line:90%
I got my youth back.

00:06:03.444 --> 00:06:04.610 align:middle line:90%
I had a lot of bills to pay.

00:06:04.610 --> 00:06:07.660 align:middle line:84%
