company in New York

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:15.730 align:middle line:84%
City that was doing a big
job in the US in my business.

00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:18.720 align:middle line:84%
And he said, maybe they
could use you in Canada.

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:20.050 align:middle line:90%
So I gave them a call.

00:06:20.050 --> 00:06:23.790 align:middle line:84%
And they said, if you're ever
in New York, give us a call.

00:06:23.790 --> 00:06:27.176 align:middle line:84%
I hung up the phone, I got in my
car, I drove to New York City.

00:06:27.176 --> 00:06:31.020 align:middle line:84%
I the next morning
put on a suit.

00:06:31.020 --> 00:06:33.864 align:middle line:90%


