00:06:35.286 --> 00:06:39.080 align:middle line:90%


00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:41.169 align:middle line:84%
I went down to their
offices on Fifth Avenue

00:06:41.169 --> 00:06:43.460 align:middle line:84%
