00:07:06.520 --> 00:07:07.320 align:middle line:90%
across Canada.

00:07:07.320 --> 00:07:10.580 align:middle line:90%


00:07:10.580 --> 00:07:14.420 align:middle line:84%
It was an incredibly
uplifting experience

00:07:14.420 --> 00:07:19.520 align:middle line:84%
to be able to look into the
eyes of a New York businessman

00:07:19.520 --> 00:07:24.970 align:middle line:84%
