can deliver Canada.

00:07:24.970 --> 00:07:29.530 align:middle line:84%
I could speak with
conviction and sincerity.

00:07:29.530 --> 00:07:30.677 align:middle line:90%
And he believed me.

00:07:30.677 --> 00:07:34.090 align:middle line:90%


00:07:34.090 --> 00:07:35.400 align:middle line:90%
That was 4 and 1/2 years ago.

00:07:35.400 --> 00:07:39.730 align:middle line:90%


00:07:39.730 --> 00:07:43.120 align:middle line:90%
