living is going

00:07:57.030 --> 00:08:00.720 align:middle line:84%
to allow a man to
walk with his head

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:05.680 align:middle line:84%
high without looking
over his shoulder

00:08:05.680 --> 00:08:09.390 align:middle line:84%
and knowing that he's
doing what's best.

00:08:09.390 --> 00:08:17.590 align:middle line:84%
It's consciousness and love
that will see us through

00:08:17.590 --> 00:08:20.000 align:middle line:90%
and that sees me through today.

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:23.650 align:middle line:84%
And as long as I live my
life honestly and simply,

00:08:23.650 --> 00:08:26.710 align:middle line:84%
I can fall asleep at night,
and I can get up in the morning

00:08:26.710 --> 00:08:27.954 align:middle line:90%
